# Script
#     fireFoam
#
# Description
#     Script to inform the user that fireFoam has been replaced by the
#     more general buoyantReactingFoam solver.
#
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------

cat << EOF

The fireFoam solver has solver has been replaced by the more general
buoyantReactingFoam solver, which supports buoyant compressible
reacting flow coupled to multiple run-time-selectable lagrangian clouds and
surface film modelling.

See the following cases for examples transferred from fireFoam:

    \$FOAM_TUTORIALS/combustion/buoyantReactingFoam/RAS

EOF

#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
